    <Content contentid="4241" contenttypeid="STAFF" desc="Staff">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>One of the great joys of staying at Villa Saanti is the impeccable service delivered by dedicated, professionally trained staff. This smiling team ensures you’ll have everything you want, when you want it. Their warm, friendly service can be tailored to meet your specific requirements. Just inform the villa manager of your desired staff presence – for example, at mealtimes only, or on hand to serve snacks and drinks throughout the day – and service will be tailored accordingly.</p>]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[VILLA MANAGER]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[Villa Saanti’s manager is your main point of contact with staff. It’s his job is to oversee and coordinate the staff and property and to assist you during your stay.<br />]]></Description>
