        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[CHEF ]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[The villa’s chef excels in the preparation and presentation of Thai, Asian and Western favourites. He will create dishes from the villa’s wide suggestion menu, or can prepare special dishes on request, also taking care of health and dietary requirements.]]></Description>
